---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — nevrai" description="Solo maker based in Georgia, building AI products with AI agents.">
  <h1 class="text-sm mb-2 text-(--color-text-dim)">## About</h1>

  <div class="prose text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-(--color-text)">
    <p>Solo maker based in Georgia.</p>

    <p>
      I build AI products using AI agents. Not in the "I use ChatGPT sometimes" way.
      I run a custom orchestration system called <strong>Factory OS</strong> — 15 specialized agent roles
      that handle everything from code generation to deployment to product research.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Claude Code</strong> is my IDE, CEO, and deployment pipeline.
      It writes the code, reviews it, tests it, and commits it.
      I make product decisions and approve changes.
    </p>

    <p>
      The result: 6 products running on $15/month of infrastructure.
      No employees. No meetings. No Slack channels. Just me, a terminal, and a lot of AI agents.
    </p>

    <p>
      I believe the future of software is small teams (or solo makers) amplified by AI.
      Not AI replacing humans — AI making one person as productive as a team of ten.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-sm mt-8 mb-4 text-(--color-text-dim)">## Links</h2>

    <ul class="space-y-2 list-none p-0">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/nevrai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> — Open source and project repos</li>
      <li><a href="https://x.com/nevrai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X / Twitter</a> — Build in public updates</li>
      <li><a href="mailto:hey@nevrai.com">hey@nevrai.com</a> — For anything else</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-sm mt-8 mb-4 text-(--color-text-dim)">## Now</h2>

    <ul class="space-y-2 list-none p-0">
      <li>Launching InkCloak (AI text detector + humanizer)</li>
      <li>Building AICPO (Cursor for product research)</li>
      <li>Shipping 199 programmatic SEO pages across 5 tool sites</li>
      <li>Setting up a Georgian IE for international payments</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
